; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/darling.md

% darling, linux

# Run a builtin command
darling shell <uname>

# Run a specific program with arguments
darling shell <path_to_program> {{program_argument_1 program_argument_2 ...}}

# Open a macOS shell
darling shell

# Shutdown the service
darling shutdown
